title: Asylum - Committed (EP)   mp3  320kbps   ak2014
description:
Asylum - Committed (EP)   mp3  320kbps  ak2014What we got...Texan death metal horde Asylum are proud to announce the release of their first proper recording, the Committed EP.

Committed features six blistering, absolutely vile tracks that clock in just under 30 minutes. These blasphemous hymns showcase a band who have honed their skills for the sole purpose of unleashing face-shredding madness upon the world.

ormed in Fort Worth, Texas in 2011, Asylum creatively delivers audible personification of the enigmatic human psyche by a medium of technical death metal, heavily influenced by old school thrash and black metal. With Committed, Asylum are paving the way for a new perspective on atmospheric and technical death metal.



Committed Tracklisting:
1. Dream Oracle
2. Welcome
3. Acidic Bath Immersion
4. Dimensional Fertilization
5. Moonlit Rite
6. Committed

Always willing to give anybody from Texas a shot cause everything from there is supposed to be bigger and faster well in Metal its got to be.....seed....seed....seed.....Texas seed.....
